The evidence with the title 'John McCain on Government Reform ' says McCain said, "we can't do this earmarking and pork-barreling if we're ever going to be careful and serious stewards of the taxpayers ' dollars." Pork is one  ...  ... McCain said , “ i 'm proud to tell you, in 24 years as a member of Congress, i have never asked for nor received a single earmark or pork barrel project for my state . ”.
